}

functions.py -> Code Generator: registry {
  style.stroke-dash: 4
}

SAS Code -> Tokenizer: raw code
Tokenizer -> Parser: tokens
Parser -> Code Generator: AST
Code Generator -> Snowflake SQL: SQL

